title: Generative AI on Vertex AI - Generative AI prompt samples

# Generative AI on Vertex AI - Generative AI prompt samples
Choose a sample to view an example of a prompt and a response from one of Google's generative AI models.
You can use the Google Cloud console or the Vertex AI API to query a model with different parameter values to test and compare their results. For more information, see [Test text prompts](/vertex-ai/generative-ai/docs/text/test-text-prompts) .
